---
title: Pea & Asparagus Gnocchi with Tarragon & Brown Butter
description: Gnocchi and brown butter are a match made in flavour heaven! A creamy tarragon-scented sauce brings a light anise flavor to the dish that's perfect with crisp asparagus and sweet peas. This dish is so speedy, maybe you'll even have time to make dessert!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/55253ff86ced6e855a8b4568.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/55253ff86ced6e855a8b4568.pdf
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/pea-and-asparagus-gnocchi-55253ff86ced6e855a8b4568
author: HelloFresh
time required: 20 minutes
